					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Video game storage media larger than 64 MB, the size of the biggest N64 Game Pak, tend to be block devices such as optical discs or DS cards. So perhaps for matches farther than 64 MB, you can optimize for 512-byte offsets, as that's the size of a sector on most block devices.</div>

